  <brief_title>A Study of Methods to Reduce Anxiety in Preoperative Elective Surgical Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of Methods to Reduce Anxiety in Preoperative Elective Surgical Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
